        -:  963:// INTERNAL IMPLEMENTATION - DO NOT USE.
        -:  964://
        -:  965:// GTEST_CHECK_ is an all-mode assert. It aborts the program if the condition
        -:  966:// is not satisfied.
        -:  967://  Synopsys:
        -:  968://    GTEST_CHECK_(boolean_condition);
        -:  969://     or
